00037 #ifndef LUSTRE_INTENT_H
00038 #define LUSTRE_INTENT_H
00039 
00040 /* intent IT_XXX are defined in lustre/include/obd.h */
00041 
00042 struct lookup_intent {
00043         int                      it_op;
00044         int                      it_create_mode;
00045         __u64                    it_flags;
00046         int                      it_disposition;
00047         int                      it_status;
00048         __u64                    it_lock_handle;
00049         __u64                    it_lock_bits;
00050         int                      it_lock_mode;
00051         int                      it_remote_lock_mode;
00052         __u64                    it_remote_lock_handle;
00053         struct ptlrpc_request   *it_request;
00054         unsigned int             it_lock_set:1;
00055 };
00056 
00057 static inline int it_disposition(const struct lookup_intent *it, int flag)
00058 {
00059         return it->it_disposition & flag;
00060 }
00061 
00062 static inline void it_set_disposition(struct lookup_intent *it, int flag)
00063 {
00064         it->it_disposition |= flag;
00065 }
00066 
00067 static inline void it_clear_disposition(struct lookup_intent *it, int flag)
00068 {
00069         it->it_disposition &= ~flag;
00070 }
00071 
00072 #endif
